{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c6288f9cf","title":"关于请郭沫若修改《到韶山》《登庐山》两首诗给胡乔木的两封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"98bdaaa7a9","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"f272a6f109","index":1,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"5c6288f9cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"3fd96bb002","name":"胡乔木","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"650d3dc7ce","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"郭沫若，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、政协全国委员会副主席、中国文学艺术界联合会主席。"},{"id":"b256616f6a","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡乔木，当时任毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"132ed286a7","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指毛泽东1959年6月写的《七律·到韶山》和7月1日写的《七律·登庐山》两首诗。"},{"id":"399f28a9c9","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指《七律·到韶山》一诗中“红旗卷起农奴戴，黑手高悬霸主鞭”一句。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e0f3e137e1","type":"title","text":"关于请郭沫若修改《到韶山《登庐山》两首诗给胡乔木的两封信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"650d3dc7ce","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"b256616f6a","type":"paragraph","text":"诗两首，请你送给郭沫若同志一阅，看有什么毛病没有？加以笔削，是为至要。主题是为了反石倾鼓干劲的，是为了惩治反觉、反总路线、反大跃进、反人民公社的。主题虽好，诗意无多，只有几句较好一些的，例如“云横九派浮黄鹤”之类。诗难，不易写，经历者如鱼饮水，冷暖自知，不足为外人道也。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"132ed286a7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"399f28a9c9","type":"paragraph","text":"九月七日乔木同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"cd5857ab54","type":"paragraph","text":"沫若同志两信都读，给了我启发。两诗又改了一点字句，请再送陈沫若一观，请他再予审改，以其意见告我为盼。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"3b24b5ac76","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"ac5bc29cfa","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十三日早上","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"},{"id":"9df629a9a0","type":"paragraph","text":"“霸主”指蒋介石。这一联写那个时期的阶级斗争。通首写三十二年的历史。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf"}],"page":{"id":"30ce19297b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5c6288f9cf","start":353,"end":354}}}},"__N_SSG":true}